#. <section class="sutta" id="sn23.10"><article><div class="hgroup"><p class="division">
msgctxt "sn23.10:0.1"
msgid "Saṃyutta Nikāya 23"
msgstr "Linked Discourses 23"

#. </p><p>
msgctxt "sn23.10:0.2"
msgid "1. Paṭhamamāravagga"
msgstr "1. About Māra"

#. </p><h1>
msgctxt "sn23.10:0.3"
msgid "10. Dutiyachandarāgasutta"
msgstr "10. Desire and Greed (2nd)"

#. </h1></div><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc1"></a>
msgctxt "sn23.10:1.1"
msgid "Sāvatthinidānaṃ."
msgstr "At Sāvatthī."

msgctxt "sn23.10:1.2"
msgid "Ekamantaṃ nisinnaṃ kho āyasmantaṃ rādhaṃ bhagavā etadavoca:"
msgstr "When Venerable Rādha was seated to one side, the Buddha said to him:"

msgctxt "sn23.10:1.3"
msgid ""
"“rūpe kho, rādha, yo chando yo rāgo yā nandī yā taṇhā ye upayupādānā cetaso "
"adhiṭṭhānābhinivesānusayā, te pajahatha."
msgstr ""
"“Rādha, you should give up any desire, greed, relishing, and craving for "
"form; and any attraction, grasping, mental dedication, insistence, and "
"underlying tendencies."

msgctxt "sn23.10:1.4"
msgid ""
"Evaṃ taṃ rūpaṃ pahīnaṃ bhavissati ucchinnamūlaṃ tālāvatthukataṃ "
"anabhāvaṅkataṃ āyatiṃ anuppādadhammaṃ."
msgstr ""
"Thus that form will be given up, cut off at the root, made like a palm "
"stump, obliterated, and unable to arise in the future."

msgctxt "sn23.10:1.5"
msgid ""
"Vedanāya yo chando yo rāgo yā nandī yā taṇhā ye upayupādānā cetaso "
"adhiṭṭhānābhinivesānusayā, te pajahatha."
msgstr ""
"You should give up any desire, greed, relishing, and craving for feeling …"

msgctxt "sn23.10:1.6"
msgid ""
"Evaṃ sā vedanā pahīnā bhavissati ucchinnamūlā tālāvatthukatā anabhāvaṅkatā "
"āyatiṃ anuppādadhammā."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "sn23.10:1.7"
msgid "Saññāya …"
msgstr "perception …"

msgctxt "sn23.10:1.8"
msgid ""
"saṅkhāresu yo chando yo rāgo yā nandī yā taṇhā ye upayupādānā cetaso "
"adhiṭṭhānābhinivesānusayā, te pajahatha."
msgstr "choices …"

msgctxt "sn23.10:1.9"
msgid ""
"Evaṃ te saṅkhārā pahīnā bhavissanti ucchinnamūlā tālāvatthukatā "
"anabhāvaṅkatā āyatiṃ anuppādadhammā."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "sn23.10:1.10"
msgid ""
"Viññāṇe yo chando yo rāgo yā nandī yā taṇhā ye upayupādānā cetaso "
"adhiṭṭhānābhinivesānusayā, te pajahatha."
msgstr ""
"consciousness; and any attraction, grasping, mental dedication, insistence, "
"and underlying tendencies."

msgctxt "sn23.10:1.11"
msgid ""
"Evaṃ taṃ viññāṇaṃ pahīnaṃ bhavissati ucchinnamūlaṃ tālāvatthukataṃ "
"anabhāvaṅkataṃ āyatiṃ anuppādadhamman”ti."
msgstr ""
"Thus that consciousness will be given up, cut off at the root, made like a "
"palm stump, obliterated, and unable to arise in the future.”"

#. </p><p class="endsection">
msgctxt "sn23.10:1.12"
msgid "Dasamaṃ."
msgstr ""

#. </p><p class="endsection">
msgctxt "sn23.10:1.13"
msgid "Rādhasaṃyuttassa paṭhamamāravaggo."
msgstr ""

#. </p><blockquote class="uddanagatha"><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc2"></a>
msgctxt "sn23.10:2.1"
msgid "Māro satto bhavanetti,"
msgstr ""

#. <br>
msgctxt "sn23.10:2.2"
msgid "pariññeyyā samaṇā duve;"
msgstr ""

#. <br>
msgctxt "sn23.10:2.3"
msgid "Sotāpanno arahā ca,"
msgstr ""

#. <br>
msgctxt "sn23.10:2.4"
msgid "chandarāgāpare duveti."
msgstr ""
